                                tristan rotateAntiClockwise angle=10 t=300
                                    sophie changeSprite surprised_speak
                                    charles changeSprite mildtakenaback

frame
    tristan changeSprite struggle
    sophie changeSprite worried_speak
    charles changeSprite serious
    sophie preSpeak
        sophie speak Are you alright?
            sophie changeSprite worried
frame
    tristan changeSprite struggle_speak
    tristan preSpeak
        tristan speak I-
            tristan wait 300
                tristan contSpeak I must find the constable...

frame
    charles changeSprite worried
    tristan speak Don't have
        tristan wait 400
            tristan speak much time...
                tristan changeSprite struggle
frame
      charles changeSprite worried_speak
      charles preSpeak
        charles speak What's going on?
            charles wait 400
                charles contSpeaking You're looking awfully pale.
                    charles changeSprite worried
frame
    tristan changeSprite struggle_speak
    tristan preSpeak
        tristan speak Winery...
            tristan wait 300
                tristan contSpeak poisoned...
                    sophie changeSprite surprised_speak
                    charles changeSprite mildtakenaback
                    tristan wait 600
                        tristan contSpeak Must save the others and boss...
                            tristan changeSprite struggle
frame
    charles changeSprite serious_speak
    charles preSpeak
        charles speak Pull yourself together!
            charles wait 400
                charles contSpeak What in the world happened?

macro cough character
    character changeSprite painexclaim_speak
    character scale x=1.02 y=1.02 skip=false t=80
        character changeSprite struggle
        character scale skip=false t=80
            character wait 200
frame
    tristan changeSprite struggle_speak
    tristan preSpeak
        tristan speak Bandits,
            tristan wait 300
                tristan contSpeak with 'M' tattoos.
                    sophie changeSprite scared
                    charles changeSprite worried

frame
    tristan speak They've kidnapped Mr. Broski-
    cough tristan
        cough tristan
            cough tristan
frame
    tristan changeSprite struggle_speak
    tristan say They took over Brostikine winery and poisoned the wine!
frame
    tristan speak They want to kill the village!
    cough tristan
        cough tristan
            cough tristan
frame
    sophie changeSprite scared_speak
    sophie preSpeak
        sophie speak That's terrible!
            charles changeSprite thinking
frame
    sophie changeSprite worried_speak
    sophie speak Where's the constable?
        sophie wait 300
            sophie contSpeak We'll bring you there,
                sophie wait 400
                    sophie contSpeak you're in no shape to walk alone.
                        sophie changeSprite worried

frame
    tristan changeSprite struggle_speak
    tristan preSpeak
        tristan speak I-
            tristan wait 400
                tristan contSpeak I'm not...
                    tristan wait 300
                        tristan contSpeak sure.
frame
    tristan speak My head hurts...

frame
    tristanDeathCG bringAboveOverlay
        tristanDeathCG bringToFront
            tristanDeathCG appear t=500
    tristan speak Ah!

frame
    tristan speak ...

frame
    tristan speak I-
        tristan wait 400
            tristan contSpeak I don't think I can make it...

frame
    tristan speak They fed me poison when they caught me escaping...

frame
    tristan speak ...and wanted to hunt me for sport...

frame
    tristan speak Too bad for them, I run fast...

frame
    tristan speak ...

frame
    tristan speak Ahh,
        tristan wait 300
            tristan contSpeak msg=it's gotten so dark... t=1200 skip=false

frame
    tristan speak Tell the constable for me,
        tristan wait 600
            tristan contSpeak msg=can't let those thugs have their way... t=600

frame
    //tristan looks at player
    tristan speak (Looks at player) I spat out some of the poison into a vial...

frame
    tristan speak msg=Take it. t=400
        tristan wait 400
            tristan contSpeak msg=I hope it is useful... t=700
                brostika displayText msg=You have received a vial of poison.
frame
    tristan speak (eyes closed)...

frame
    sophie preSpeak
        sophie speak Tristan?
            sophie wait 700
                sophie speak Tristan!

frame
    charles preSpeak
        charles speak He's
            charles wait 300
                charles contSpeak stopped breathing...

frame
    charles speak I'm sorry, I should have tried to do something for him.

//frame
//    charles speak He was a kind soul,
//        charles wait 300
//            charles contSpeak worrying about his fellow workers till the very end.

frame
    sophie preSpeak
        sophie speak Poor Tristan,
            sophie wait 300
                sophie contSpeak His eyes,
                    sophie wait 300
                        sophie contSpeak they were so angry and scared.

frame
    sophie speak Those thugs must have really tortured him to make him hate them like that.

frame
    sophie speak I hope he is at peace now.

frame
    charles preSpeak
        charles speak What are you doing, Sophie?

frame
    sophie preSpeak
        sophie speak Brostikans believe that if you tie a thread to the pinky of someone who passes on,

frame
    sophie contSpeak their spirit will not disappate and they will be able to watch over their loved ones.

frame
    charles speak ...

frame
    charles preSpeak
        charles speak You're as knowledgeable about local superstitions as always...

frame
    sophie preSpeak
        sophie speak They're not superstitions, Charles!
            sophie endSpeak

frame
    tristanDeathCG disappear t=500
        sophie changeSprite hesitate_speak
        charles changeSprite worried
        sophie preSpeak
            sophie speak Can you carry Tristan, Charles?

frame
    sophie changeSprite gazeindistance_speak
    sophie speak We should hand his body to the constable so that he can be given a proper burial.

frame
    sophie speak Besides,
        sophie wait 300
            sophie contSpeak we can't possibly leave him with the corpses of his pursuers here.
                sophie changeSprite sad
frame
    charles changeSprite serious_speak
    charles preSpeak
        charles speak Yes, of course.

frame
    charles speak We'll make our way to Erithven after handing this issue over to the town guards.
        charles changeSprite serious
